reviewText: I enjoyed the dvd and would recommend it to everyone.
I bought this dvd as it has various dinosaur documentaries which are really awesome.

This DVD set has a lot of entertaining and educational programs. The two best ones are about prehistoric crocodiles and evolution of mammals. This set is definitely worth buying for those other dinosaur fans out there.
